headline: The Trade Desk (TTD) Fell Amid Strength in Broader Advertising Market
summary: Baron Funds, an investment management company, released its “Baron Technology Fund” third-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. US equities rallied in the third quarter following the previous quarter. In the third quarter, the fund returned 5.89% (Institutional Shares) but underperformed the MSCI ACWI Information Technology Index’s (the Benchmark) 12.76% […]
